½In loving memory of David Kermeen (KERMELLY) 16.1066 - 14.10.07
The seas he sailed were vast and deep.
Our thoughts of him with love, we'll keep.
As we look out over Ramsey Bay
Davy is with us, whatever the day.
Riding high on the waves of the daily tide,
We'll remember him with
LOVE & PRIDE"į
